  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Increasing commodity marketing for financial sustainability of the cooperative</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Chemakapenje cooperative will execute this project by focusing on different issues like stated below:Sourcing markets for its members to sell their farm produce (collective marketing) i.e. soya beans  sunflower  beans  maize and groundnutsAggregating farm produce for selling to off-takersStorage of farm produceSupplying inputs through loans (out-grower scheme)Buying and selling of farm produce.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The goal of the cooperative is to:To increase membership from 523 to 1 000To boost up capital to K11 000 000To conduct collective marketing for their members produceTo open a selling point at their warehouse and be selling farm inputs (Agro-dealership)</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The project plan for 2020 will focus on improving the financial management (basic record keeping) and governance system of the cooperative. They will also be helped in conducting external audits and development of a strategic plan</narrative>
  </description>
